WEBVTT

00:10.140 --> 00:11.180
CHAPTER II.

00:11.440 --> 00:13.180
THERE IS A SCIENCE OF GETTING RICH.

00:14.560 --> 00:19.420
There is a science of getting rich, and it is an exact science, like algebra or arithmetic.

00:20.120 --> 00:23.240
There are certain laws which govern the process of acquiring riches.

00:23.820 --> 00:28.240
Once these laws are learned and obeyed by any man, he will get rich with mathematical

00:28.240 --> 00:28.860
certainty.

00:29.640 --> 00:34.420
The ownership of money and property comes as a result of doing things in a certain way.

00:34.980 --> 00:40.300
Those who do things in this certain way, whether on purpose or accidentally, get rich, while

00:40.300 --> 00:45.460
those who do not do things in this certain way, no matter how hard they work or how able

00:45.460 --> 00:47.060
they are, remain poor.

00:47.940 --> 00:53.240
It is a natural law that like causes always produce like effects, and therefore any man

00:53.240 --> 00:57.840
or woman who learns to do things in this certain way will infallibly get rich.

00:58.520 --> 01:01.860
That the above statement is true is shown by the following facts.

01:02.760 --> 01:07.200
Getting rich is not a matter of environment, for if it were, all the people in certain

01:07.200 --> 01:11.800
neighborhoods would become wealthy, the people of one city would be all rich, while those

01:11.800 --> 01:16.400
of other towns would all be poor, for the inhabitants of one state would roll in wealth,

01:16.980 --> 01:19.620
while those of an adjoining state would be in poverty.

01:19.740 --> 01:24.660
But everywhere we see rich and poor living side by side, in the same environment, and

01:24.660 --> 01:26.660
often engaged in the same vocations.

01:27.100 --> 01:31.940
When two men are in the same locality and in the same business, and one gets rich while

01:31.940 --> 01:36.740
the other remains poor, it shows that getting rich is not primarily a matter of environment.

01:37.320 --> 01:42.220
Some environments may be more favorable than others, but when two men in the same business

01:42.220 --> 01:47.060
are in the same neighborhood, and one gets rich while the other fails, it indicates that

01:47.060 --> 01:50.040
getting rich is a result of doing things in a certain way.

01:50.700 --> 01:55.820
And further, the ability to do things in this certain way is not due solely to the possession

01:55.820 --> 02:00.120
of talent, for many people who have great talent remain poor, while others who have

02:00.120 --> 02:01.820
very little talent get rich.

02:02.560 --> 02:07.520
Studying the people who have got rich, we find that they are an average lot in all respects,

02:07.980 --> 02:10.700
having no greater talents or abilities than other men.

02:11.020 --> 02:15.400
It is evident that they do not get rich because they possess talents or abilities that other

02:15.400 --> 02:19.160
men have not, but because they happen to do things in a certain way.

02:19.920 --> 02:24.920
Getting rich is not the result of saving or thrift, many very penurious people are poor,

02:24.920 --> 02:27.500
while free spenders often get rich.

02:27.940 --> 02:32.660
Nor is getting rich due to doing things which others fail to do, for two men in the same

02:32.660 --> 02:37.160
business often do almost exactly the same things, and one gets rich while the other

02:37.160 --> 02:39.160
remains poor or becomes bankrupt.

02:40.140 --> 02:44.140
From all these things, we must come to the conclusion that getting rich is the result

02:44.140 --> 02:45.920
of doing things in a certain way.

02:46.640 --> 02:51.600
If getting rich is the result of doing things in a certain way, and if like causes always

02:51.600 --> 02:56.720
produce like effects, then any man or woman who can do things in that way can become rich,

02:57.040 --> 03:00.400
and the whole matter is brought within the domain of exact science.

03:01.180 --> 03:05.960
The question arises here whether this certain way may not be so difficult that only a few

03:05.960 --> 03:06.900
may follow it.

03:07.140 --> 03:11.560
This cannot be true, as we have seen, so far as natural ability is concerned.

03:12.120 --> 03:15.160
Talented people get rich, and blockheads get rich.

03:15.960 --> 03:19.520
Intellectually brilliant people get rich, and very stupid people get rich.

03:19.520 --> 03:23.940
Physically strong people get rich, and weak and sickly people get rich.

03:24.500 --> 03:28.180
Some degree of ability to think and understand is, of course, essential.

03:28.720 --> 03:33.500
But in so far natural ability is concerned, any man or woman who has sense enough to read

03:33.500 --> 03:36.040
and understand these words can certainly get rich.

03:36.800 --> 03:39.420
Also, we have seen that it is not a matter of environment.

03:40.000 --> 03:44.600
Location counts for something, one would not go to the heart of the Sahara and expect to

03:44.600 --> 03:45.780
do successful business.

03:46.320 --> 03:51.080
Getting rich involves the necessity of dealing with man, and of being where there are people

03:51.080 --> 03:51.840
to deal with.

03:52.180 --> 03:56.680
And if these people are inclined to deal in the way you want to deal, so much the better.

03:57.040 --> 03:59.340
But that is about as far as environment goes.

03:59.860 --> 04:02.880
If anybody else in your town can get rich, so can you.

04:03.200 --> 04:06.500
And if anybody else in your state can get rich, so can you.

04:07.180 --> 04:10.780
Again, it is not a matter of choosing some particular business or profession.

04:11.360 --> 04:14.200
People get rich in every business and in every profession.

04:14.760 --> 04:18.400
While their next-door neighbours on the same vacation remain in poverty.

04:19.220 --> 04:23.720
It is true that you will do best in a business which you like and which is congenial to you.

04:24.100 --> 04:28.140
And if you have certain talents which are well developed, you will do best in a business

04:28.140 --> 04:30.300
which calls for the exercise of those talents.

04:31.640 --> 04:35.200
Also, you will do best in a business which is suited to your locality.

04:35.540 --> 04:39.920
An ice-cream parlour would do better in a warm climate than in Greenland, and a salmon

04:39.920 --> 04:44.280
fishery would succeed better in the north-west than in Florida, where there are no salmon.

04:44.980 --> 04:49.700
But aside from these general limitations, getting rich is not dependent upon your engaging

04:49.700 --> 04:54.100
in some particular business, but upon your learning to do things in a certain way.

04:54.360 --> 04:58.280
If you are now in business and everybody else in your locality is getting rich in the same

04:58.280 --> 05:02.080
business while you are not getting rich, it is because you are not doing things in the

05:02.080 --> 05:04.200
same way that the other person is doing them.

05:04.880 --> 05:07.620
No one is prevented from getting rich by lack of capital.

05:08.200 --> 05:12.980
True, as you get capital the increase becomes more easy and rapid, but one who has capital

05:12.980 --> 05:16.600
is already rich, and does not need to consider how to become so.

05:17.060 --> 05:21.880
No matter how poor you may be, if you begin to do things in a certain way, you will begin

05:21.880 --> 05:24.580
to get rich, and you will begin to have capital.

05:25.240 --> 05:30.100
The getting of capital is a part of the process of getting rich, and it is a part of the result

05:30.100 --> 05:33.580
which invariably follows the doing of things in a certain way.

05:33.580 --> 05:37.380
You may be the poorest man on the continent, and be deeply in debt.

05:37.680 --> 05:42.500
You may have neither friends, influence, nor resources, but if you begin to do things in

05:42.500 --> 05:48.240
this way, you must infallibly begin to get rich, for like causes must produce like effects.

05:48.720 --> 05:51.000
If you have no capital, you can get capital.

05:51.480 --> 05:54.580
If you are in the wrong business, you can get into the right business.

05:55.020 --> 05:59.480
If you are in the wrong location, you can go to the right location, and you can do so

05:59.480 --> 06:04.640
in your present business and in your present location, to do things in a certain way which

06:04.640 --> 06:05.760
causes success.

